<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Cloudy" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Cloudy,</orth> overcast with clouds; properly and figuratively: <cit><quote>so do thy lips make modest Dian c. and forlorn,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 725" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 725</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>no c. show of stormy weather,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 115" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 115</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>c. Lucrece,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 115" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 115</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>c. looks,</quote> <bibl n="shak. pp 312" default="NO" valid="yes">Pilgr. 312</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>when you are c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.142" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 1, 142</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the c. cheeks of heaven,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 3.3.57" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 III, 3, 57</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>c. men,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.2.83" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 2, 83</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>c. brow,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.155" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 155</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>death,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.6.62" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 6, 62</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>wrath,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.268" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 268</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>princes,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 2.2.112" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 112</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tit 1.263" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. I, 263</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.33" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 33</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.2.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 2, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 3.6.41" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. III, 6, 41</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 3.1.46" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. III, 1, 46</bibl> <emph>(c. billow).</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>